text:
My approach has been to use the Search API searching for meetings associated to that contact, because then you can sort by whichever datetime property you would like.

curl <https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/objects/meetings/search> \
  --request POST \
  --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
  --data '{
    "filters": [
      {
        "propertyName": "associations.contact",
        "operator": "EQ",
        "value": "123"
      }
    ]
  }'
